column5: Hey...  I havent had much to report yet this season... but I have to say... during the off season we get alot of people asking if this is a fishing board...  well look at what its like here when there is fishing to be had...  Thanks to everyone whos posting pics and reports.  I'll have one shorlty .. we are making a quick trip up to Kesagami shorlty. (gotta get some decent fish in the tourney!!
Good luck!!!  Looking forward to reading all about it!  Bly
